        "created_at": "2018-10-14T21:31:42.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Nice notes, Robert,</p>\n<p>Thanks for posting; your description of the Bouchard Montrachet, which I\u2019ve had a few times in different vintages, really nails it. Interesting that you found the H-N RSV less elegant, if that\u2019s the right word than the Richebourg. How much air the did the Baroli get?</p>",
