        "cooked": "<p>Julian, definitely got some reactions to this through pm. It was a crying shame. I\u2019ve only tasted one pre-2010 PYCM Grand Cru and didn\u2019t love it so was looking forward to this, and especially a Batard. Here\u2019s a picture.<br>\n<img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/d/4/d42807fc6945d6706b2454e179bedc250f72a08b.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_5967.JPG\" data-base62-sha1=\"ugOZoex8GuMDwGpLLamSaTm2Y6T\" width=\"2700\" height=\"3600\"></p>",
